title: 2 Stoned 2 Podcast! | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano: Hey Babe! | EP 95
description:
THE BABES are off the GANJA THIS EPISODE! STONERS talking sugar and what real food is these days. Memory is tough. What effects did Nukes have on humanity? Chris makes a fool of himself at school. Shout out  @Brendan Sagalow  and his rap music. The babes start the Hey Babe National Anthem contest #HeyBabeNationalAnthem Chris admits he feels conflicted in his life. Rare rainbow cloud in China. Why lightning strikes certain people. Microsculptures are SUS. What is the human mind and what do we really know. The gut is key to your health. Walk barefoot on the reg babe itll save your life. What happens to your soul when you die? Sal talks about a new punishment on Impractical Jokers with Anthony Davis. Shout out those weird web toe shoes. Are you happy in your meat vessel? Chris hates Disney! Who poops at DISNEY!??!?!
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
